 1531                                                       ;new line number in relation to the line numbers cur-
 1532                                                       ;rently in the program buffer. The next portion of the
 1533                                                       ;program goes through the contents of the USER PRO-
 1534                                                       ;GRAM BUFFER comparing the values of the line num-
 1535                                                       ;bers already stored against the value of the line number
