 2482  1046  F2 50 10                JP	ACZERT                    ;If sign bit not set then jump ahead to do next test
 2483  1049  06 04                   MVI	B,004H                   ;If sign bit set, number in FPACC is negative. Set up
 2484  104B  2E 53                   MVI	L,OFS_SYMBOL_BUF+3                   ;For two's complement operation
