 3086  1350  FE AE        NOTPLM:	CPI	0AEH                        ;See if character represents a period (decimal point) in
 3087  1352  CA 81 13                JZ	PERIOD                    ;Input string. Jump ahead if yes.
 3088  1355  FE C5                   CPI	0C5H                     ;If not period, see if code for E as in Exponent
 3089  1357  CA 91 13                JZ	FNDEXP                    ;Jump ahead if yes.
